This repository contains README + reference metadata for the FoundryNet Forge
MCP server. The server software itself is proprietary and commercial.

Commercial license, free tier available.

- Free tier:   100 tool calls/month + 10 fire_sandbox fires lifetime, no card.
- Paid:        Pay-per-use metered billing — see https://foundrynet.io/pricing
               for live unit prices. As a rough guide: one machine sampled
               every 30 seconds runs ~$13/month; every 10 seconds ~$40/month;
               every 1 second ~$260/month. Scales linearly with machine count.
- Enterprise:  custom — foundrynet@proton.me.

